nodes.text: Timeline 16: Founding of the Republic would have been the sixteenth in the series of in-universe videos, providing backstory for the Star Wars: The Old Republic video game. The video would have been presented in the form of a record entry made in the Jedi Archives by Jedi Master Gnost-Dural.
The remaining Timeline videos were discontinued in early 2011, as the content was growing less relevant to the game.
The development of the hyperdrive expanded the known galaxy. To keep order, several star systems, formed a democratic alliance.
